- **Session logs:** Bron `.bron` one-clock filenames and README index per `.cursor/rules/session-logs.mdc`; **Editor:** Cursor · **Model:** as appropriate · voice **Rio 3**.
- **Stay durable.** Keep anything worth saving inside `~/veganreyklah2`.
